<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard Admin - Lembur B06</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/basecoat.css">
</head>
<body class="bc-body">
    <header class="bc-header bc-header--dark">
        <h1>Panel Admin Kepegawaian</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="bc-container">
        <section class="bc-card" style="margin-top: 20px; border-left: 5px solid var(--bc-primary);">
            <h2 class="bc-h2">Rekapitulasi Laporan Bulanan [cite: 55]</h2>
            <p>Akses data lembur yang telah dikonfirmasi oleh pimpinan untuk keperluan administratif.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="bc-grid" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <div class="bc-col">
                <div class="bc-card">
                    <h4 class="bc-h4">Laporan Siap Rekap</h4>
                    <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">12 Data</p>
                    <button class="bc-btn bc-btn--success bc-btn--block">Unduh Rekap (PDF/DOCX) [cite: 41, 84]</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bc-col">
                <div class="bc-card">
                    <h4 class="bc-h4">Total Jam Lembur</h4>
                    <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">48 Jam</p>
                    <button class="bc-btn bc-btn--secondary bc-btn--block">Lihat Detail Laporan</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/basecoat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>